rating_comment: Best place to stay at Mymensingh, peaceful, away from the hustle bustle of the city, beside the river Bhramhaputra. Though it is about 4km away from the main city but always preferred, toto/CNG is always available. Excellent WiFi speed and homely atmosphere. Will always choose this place if we again visit Mymensing. Thank you so much!!

info: Rating, 3 stars,  · March 2021,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: Room is clean, communication was prompt. Expecting river view room and attached bathroom but both not available so bit disappointed. Staff are helpful.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · January 2020,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: The guesthouse was so comfortable and a nice quiet place with views of the river.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · February 2019,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: Excellent hospitality, location and amenities provided by the host. You can get amazing view of river from there. Had a great time over there. Highly recommend.
